# Dataset Plan

## Study Area
Nagpur, India

## Primary Target
Land Surface Temperature (LST)

## Version 1 Features
- NDVI
- NDBI
- Land cover
- Elevation
- Water presence / water mask

## Candidate Data Sources
- Landsat 8/9
- Sentinel-2
- SRTM DEM
- Land cover dataset
- Water mask source

## Initial Time Window
Summer / high-heat period with manageable cloud cover

## Modeling Unit
Raster pixels or sampled grid cells
